<title>Special Notation</title>         
<para xml:id="C35.S1.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="1" xml:id="C35.S1.p1.s1">
(For other notation see Notation for the Special Functions.)
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C35.S1.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="2" xml:id="C35.S1.p2.s1">
All matrices are of order <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C35.S1.p2.m1">m\times m</Math> , unless specified otherwise.
</sentence>

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="2" sentence-num-in-section="3" xml:id="C35.S1.p2.s2">
All fractional or complex powers are principal values.
</sentence>

</para>

 
